  "Only nonzero entries contribute to the cofactor expansion. With 3 zeros and 1 nonzero entry in column 1, only 1 term survives, requiring just one 3x3 determinant.": "只有非零条目有助于共构因素的扩展。 第1栏有3个零和1个非零条目,只有1个任期,仅需要1个3x3决定因素。",
  "What is det([[5,0,0],[0,3,0],[0,0,7]]) using cofactor expansion?": "什么是([[5,0,0],[0,3,0],[0,0,7])使用共生因素扩张?",
