  "Expanding along row 1: 5*det([[3,0],[0,7]]) - 0 + 0 = 5*(21) = 105. Alternatively, for a diagonal matrix, det = product of diagonal = 5*3*7 = 105.": "第1行:5*det([[3,0],[0,7]) - 0+0=5*(21]=105),或者,对于对角矩阵, det = diagonal = 5*3*7 = 105。",
  "What is 'cofactor expansion' (also called Laplace expansion)?": "什么是“致因扩张”(也称为拉帕扩张)?",
  "A technique for expanding the size of a matrix": "扩大矩阵规模的技术",
  "A way to factor matrices into simpler pieces": "一种将矩阵要素化为简单件的方法",
  "A method that expresses the determinant as a weighted sum of cofactors along any row or column": "将决定因素表示为任何一行或一列的共生因素加权总和的方法",
  "A method for computing eigenvalues": "计算 eigenvalue 的方法",
  "Cofactor expansion computes det(A) by summing products of entries and their cofactors along any single row or column: det(A) = sum of a_{ij} * C_{ij}.": "Cofactor 扩展计算 det( A) , 方法是在任何单行或列上对条目及其共构物进行合成: dot( A) = aij} * Cij} 的和 。",
  "What is a 'submatrix' in the context of cofactor expansion?": "在共生因素扩张的背景下,“子矩阵”是什么?",
  "The upper-left block of the matrix": "矩阵的上左上左部分",
  "The matrix obtained by deleting one row and one column from the original matrix": "从原始矩阵中删去一行和一列后取得的矩阵",
  "Any matrix smaller than the original": "任何比原表小于原表的任何矩阵",
  "A matrix formed by the pivot entries": "由枢轴条目构成的矩阵",
  "In cofactor expansion, the submatrix for entry a_{ij} is the (n-1)x(n-1) matrix obtained by deleting row i and column j.": "在焦因扩展中,条目aj}的子矩阵是通过删除第i行和j列获得的(n-1x(n-1))矩阵。",
  "What does the term 'Laplace expansion' refer to?": "“Laplace 扩张”一词指的是什么?",
  "The Taylor series expansion of a matrix function": "泰勒系列扩大矩阵功能",
  "Another name for cofactor expansion of determinants, named after Pierre-Simon Laplace": "以Pierre-Simon Laplace命名的决定因素共同因素扩展的另一个名称",
  "A method for solving differential equations using matrices": "使用矩阵表解决差别方程的方法",
  "The Laplace transform applied to a matrix": "适用于矩阵的 Laplace 变换",
  "Laplace expansion is the formal name for cofactor expansion. Laplace proved that expanding along any row or column yields the same determinant.": "Laplace 扩展是共生因素扩展的正式名称。 Laplace 证明沿着任何一行或一列扩展会产生相同的决定因素 。",
  "What does the 'cofactor matrix' (matrix of cofactors) consist of?": "“ 系数矩阵”( 系数矩阵) 包括哪些内容 ?",
  "A matrix of all minors without sign adjustments": "一份无签名调整的未成年人信息总库",
  "The original entries multiplied by -1": "原始条目乘以 -1",
  "The inverse of the original matrix": "原矩阵的逆数",
  "The matrix where each entry a_{ij} is replaced by its cofactor C_{ij}": "每个条目aj} 被其共构方 Cj} 替换的矩阵",
  "The cofactor matrix has entry (i,j) equal to C_{ij} = (-1)^(i+j) * M_{ij}. Its transpose is the adjugate (classical adjoint) matrix.": "共振矩阵的条目(i,j)等于 Cij} = (-1) (i+j) * Mij}。 它的转换是辅助(经典联合)矩阵。",
  "What is the 'recursive nature' of cofactor expansion?": "共生因素扩张的“稳定性质”是什么?",
  "The matrix must be expanded along every row": "表格必须按每一行扩展",
  "The expansion must be repeated until all entries are positive": "必须重复扩展, 直到所有条目均为正",
  "The same formula is applied to progressively smaller matrices until reaching a base case": "同一公式适用于逐渐缩小的基数矩阵,直至达到基数",
  "The determinant is computed by recursion on the matrix size, but only for symmetric matrices": "决定因素通过对矩阵大小的重复计算来计算,但仅对称矩阵计算。",
  "Cofactor expansion reduces an nxn determinant to a sum of (n-1)x(n-1) determinants. Each of these can be expanded further, recursing down to 2x2 or 1x1 base cases.": "共生体膨胀将nxn的决定因素减为总和(n-1x(n-1))的决定因素,其中每一种都可以进一步扩大,重现为2x2或1x1基例。",
  "What does 'expanding along a row' mean?": "\"一连串扩张\"是什么意思?",
  "Computing det(A) = sum of a_{ij} * C_{ij} for j = 1 to n, where i is the chosen row": "j = 1 至 n, 其中i 是所选择的行",
  "Multiplying all entries in the row by the row number": "将行内所有条目乘以行号",
  "Inserting a new row into the matrix": "在矩阵中插入新行",
  "Adding entries of the row together": "将行条目同时添加",
  "Expanding along row i means fixing the row index i and summing over all columns j: det(A) = a_{i1}C_{i1} + a_{i2}C_{i2} + ... + a_{in}C_{in}.": "沿行扩展 i 意指固定行索引 i , 并在所有 j 栏上进行缩放 : dat( A) = ai1} C1} + a2} C2} +... + ain} Cin} +... + ain} Cin} 。",
  "What is the 'adjugate' (classical adjoint) matrix?": "什么是“adjuggate”(古典联合)矩阵?",
  "The row-reduced form of the matrix": "矩阵的减行格式",
  "The transpose of the matrix of cofactors": "共同要素矩阵转换",
  "The conjugate of the matrix": "矩阵的组合",
  "The matrix of minors": "未成年人矩阵表",
  "The adjugate adj(A) is the transpose of the cofactor matrix. It satisfies A * adj(A) = det(A) * I, which gives the formula A^(-1) = adj(A)/det(A).": "adj(A)是同源矩阵的转换,它符合A* adj(A) = dot(A) * I, 它给出的公式是A(-1) = adj(A)/det(A)。",
  "What is the computational complexity of computing an nxn determinant by cofactor expansion?": "通过同源物扩张计算 nxn 决定因素的计算复杂性是什么?",
  "O(n^3)": "O(n%3)",
  "O(n!)": "O(n) !",
  "O(n^2)": "O(n%2)",
  "O(n log n)": "O(n log n)",
  "Naive cofactor expansion has O(n!) complexity because each nxn determinant spawns n determinants of size (n-1), leading to n! total operations. This is why Gaussian elimination (O(n^3)) is preferred for large n.": "由于每个nxn决定因素产生大小(n-1)n的决定因素(n-1),从而导致n!总操作,因此N(n)(n)(n)具有O(n)的复杂性。因此,大n(n)(O(n)3)更倾向于消除高斯(O(n)3)。",
  "What is an 'alien cofactor' expansion?": "什么是“外星人共生因素”扩张?",
  "A cofactor expansion that uses complex numbers": "使用复杂数字的共因子扩展",
  "An expansion using entries from one row and cofactors from a different row, which always equals zero": "使用从一行开始的条目和从另一行开始的共构因素进行扩展,这些参数总是等于零",
  "A cofactor expansion along the diagonal": "沿着对角线的共因子扩张",
  "An expansion technique for non-square matrices": "非平方矩阵表的扩展技术",
  "If you multiply entries from row i by cofactors of row k (where i != k), the sum is always zero. This is used to prove the formula A * adj(A) = det(A) * I.": "如果将一行的条目乘以行 k( i $= k) 的同源因素, 则总和总是为零。 用于证明公式 A * adj( A) = dot( A) * I 。",
  "What is the connection between cofactors and the inverse of a matrix?": "共同因素与矩阵逆向之间的联系是什么?",
  "A^(-1) = adj(A) / det(A), where adj(A) is the transpose of the cofactor matrix": "A(-1) = adj(A) / det(A),其中adj(A) 是共构物矩阵的转换",
  "Cofactors are only used for 2x2 inverses": "2x2 的反函数只使用共量",
  "A^(-1) = det(A) * adj(A)": "A(-1) = det( A) * adj( A)",
  "A^(-1) equals the cofactor matrix": "A(-1) 等于共元素矩阵",
  "The inverse formula A^(-1) = (1/det(A)) * adj(A) uses cofactors directly. The (i,j) entry of A^(-1) is C_{ji}/det(A).": "A(-1) = (1/det(A)) * adj(A) 直接使用同源物。 A(-1) 的(i,j) 条目是 Cji}/det(A) 。",
  "A structural engineer needs det of a 3x3 stiffness matrix [[10, -3, 0], [-3, 10, -3], [0, -3, 10]]. She expands along row 1. What is the first term (from entry a_{11})?": "结构工程师需要3x3硬度矩阵[[10,3,0],[3,10,3,3],[0,3,10]]。",
  "10 * 91 = 910": "10 * 91=910",
  "10 * (100 - 9) = 910": "10*(100-9)=910",
  "10 * 100 = 1000": "10 * 100=1000",
  "10 * (10 - 3) = 70": "10* (10-3) = 70",
  "First term: a_{11} * C_{11} = 10 * det([[10,-3],[-3,10]]) = 10 * (100 - 9) = 10 * 91 = 910.": "第一个学期:a11} * C11} = 10 * det([[10,3],[3,10]) = 10 * (100 - 9) = 10 * 91 = 910。",
  "A chemist computing a 4x4 determinant notices column 2 has entries [0, 5, 0, 0]. How many 3x3 cofactors must she evaluate?": "计算4x4决定性通知第2栏的化学家有条目[0,5,0,0]。她必须评估多少3x3共构因素?",
  "Only the nonzero entry (5 in row 2) contributes. She needs just 1 cofactor: (-1)^(2+2) * 5 * det(3x3 submatrix with row 2, col 2 removed).": "只有非零条目( 第2行中的5项)才起作用。 她只需要一个共构因素 :( 1) ( 2+2) * 5 det( 3x3) 子矩阵, 而第 2 行 2 Col 2 则被删除 ) 。",
  "An audio engineer has a 3x3 mixing matrix [[1, 0, 0], [0.5, 1, 0], [0.3, 0.2, 1]]. She computes det by expanding along column 3. Which entries contribute?": "音频工程师有一个3x3混合矩阵[[[1,0,0],[0.5,1,0],[0.3,0.2,1]],[0.3,0.2,1]]。",
  "Only the entry in row 3 (which is 1)": "只有第3行的条目(即1)",
  "Only entries in rows 1 and 2": "只有第1行和第2行中的条目",
  "All three entries in column 3": "第3栏的所有三个条目",
  "None, because it is lower triangular": "无,因为它是下三角形",
  "Column 3 has entries 0, 0, 1. Only the third entry (1) is nonzero, so only one term contributes. det = 1*(-1)^(3+3)*det([[1,0],[0.5,1]]) = 1*1*1 = 1.": "第3列有第0、0、1条目。只有第3项(1)为非零,因此只有一个术语。 det = 1*(-1){(3+3)**det[[1,0],[0.5,1]]) = 1*1*1=1。",
  "A physicist needs det([[2,-1,0,0],[-1,2,-1,0],[0,-1,2,-1],[0,0,-1,2]]). She expands along row 1 and gets the first two terms as 2*det(3x3) and 1*det(3x3). After full computation, what is the determinant?": "物理学家需要执行([[[2,1,0,0,0],[[1,2,1,1],[0,1,2,1],[0,0,1,1,1])。她沿着第1行扩展,头两个任期为2*det(3x3)和1*det(3x3)。在充分计算后,什么是决定因素?",
