  "A computer science student is asked to count operations for a 5x5 determinant via cofactor expansion. She knows each step reduces to five 4x4 determinants. Roughly how many 2x2 determinants will she compute in total (worst case)?": "计算机科学学生被要求通过共振扩展来计算5x5决定因素的操作量。 她知道每一步都会降低到5 4x4决定因素。 她估计总共将计算多少 2x2 决定因素( worst case ) ?",
